Z","msg":"我仲慘，叫好彩有d姿色，日日比老母嘈話快d去識有錢佬嫁左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話屋企冇錢收既婚唔比結，賣女咁既款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我講你老母"},{"pid":"839f4cdbcb295f5be3e6ed04f180e81b60f8a95d","tid":2160512,"uid":283152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc22194c772f85c2246adb357223e5161ca94bb3","tid":2160512,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"其實香港好多人唔明白貧窮係幾可怕，你永遠彌補唔返！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"你睇施老闆有幾憎聖誕節就知啦"},{"pid":"6e7dde8595e1d780032e549e3ebab060944e0163","tid":2160512,"uid":93615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友細個從來唔讀書，入唔到大學只可以讀asso, grad 完出黎打份濕鳩文職，得萬零蚊<br />\n不過唔緊要，佢老豆開幾間餐廳又有酒吧，大陸有啲生意咁，前幾年一grad 就買咗層樓俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢上年結埋婚，黎緊計劃生小朋友。<br />\n反而我呢啲窮撚，細個死讀爛讀入到u,到而家做緊份睇落唔錯嘅工作，但咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓又買唔到住，結婚都唔洗諗，講緊有錢嘅人已經做晒買樓結婚呢幾樣，領先啲窮撚幾步<br />\n上個月我老豆啲兄弟過咗身，老豆仲問我可唔可以借一萬蚊俾佢周轉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢無錢做皂金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3c53b37b2d49bf5b0ff93172c6f3d036428b36","tid":2160512,"uid":185565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"家家有本難念的經<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮人的經更加難念"},{"pid":"ff7ccf7ff0f8bf7413211f7d8b2d4fa82deeb84d","tid":2160512,"uid":197637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"最慘係同班有啲錢既講窮撚點慘<br />\n<br />\n只會覺得窮撚負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla